- Curry.Base.MessageMonad: Introduce new type class combining the features of
  - Reporting of warnings
  - Error propagation
  - Exception handling
  - IO capabilities

  A typical instance may be:
  newtype KicsT m a = KicsT { unKicsT :: WriterT [Message] (ErrorT Message (m (IO a))) }
  or something similar

- The Read and Show instances of Idents do not correspond